{"tid":2065023,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都係好驚打風","createTime":"2020-06-15T08:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T15:21:57.000Z","uid":66699,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"137bd747745ef2dcd0b1319dd16639ad48341ba9","tid":2065023,"uid":66699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"每次打風都會好驚<br />\n有種好不安好唔穩定嘅感覺<br />\n成日凝住啲嘢會吹爛吹走<br />\n就算閂窗都無用，一聽到聲都會驚<br />\n<br />\n利申 絲<br />\n想知淨係女仔先會驚定係男仔都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02869233aa9d5a31cb3e51bb55276fb88c87ea49","tid":2065023,"uid":66699,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:43:37.000Z","msg":"係咪大家都唔驚打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc2076262424c2d4152cefc20f191b240acd5d1","tid":2065023,"uid":165749,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"我驚打唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e15c3144ed27f7a95d908b0c4d311b8eec0b9b5","tid":2065023,"uid":251732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"我唔想再經歷山竹級颶風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04238c99c53cb6a61297a642215295fb753ced27","tid":2065023,"uid":211822,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"利申巴<br />\n以前唔驚 山竹果次開始識驚<br />\n見住啲風同雨向橫飛勁痴線<br />\n一路聽住勁大風聲之餘 仲間唔時聽到其他單位爆玻璃<br />\n成日都形住自己房個大玻璃會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb83293124ad413bb810d9dfd5c1b7b572df984","tid":2065023,"uid":66699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edc2076262424c2d4152cefc20f191b240acd5d1","tid":2065023,"uid":165749,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"我驚打唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"唔洗