yTime":"2020-06-15T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"驚唔驚行雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbef58a6e24303b50e29094cc318d6ca39408bf","tid":2065023,"uid":52371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32d2ee8b60b5deb3e9889fb31020fcbe4174ff36","tid":2065023,"uid":66699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04eb4865685c6cb9f1e5dc797f057e9dcdf7506b","tid":2065023,"uid":52371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a383acc8d69200d522659952326375771e996ccf","tid":2065023,"uid":66699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"絲打你係咪同我一樣<br />\n本身性格都比較敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"你舉下例子睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"對感情關係上好敏感，無論係友情定愛情<br />\n會在意好人家感受等等<br />\n又或者自己心入面會有小劇場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"我會好容易就去諗對方對我係咩<br />\n會去猜疑對方有冇其他意思<br />\n但我唔會好擺係心 <br />\n我只係個一刻在乎一陣<br />\n好快就唔當一回事<br />\n愛情就比較真係在乎嘅<br />\n友情睇好化<br />\n家人都睇好化<br />\n<br />\n內心小劇場真係可以一日上幾十集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會成日驚，如果我呢一刻唔洗多20秒手，會唔會殺唔死病菌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁中咗就好唔抵啦⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n搭小巴一唔小心摸到扶手，就要消毒消毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企人咳幾聲又會驚<br />\n自己沖完熱水涼個身比較興又會驚一驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大風時坐小巴又會幻想會唔會有怪風吹反架小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上小劇場好常出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩係我好快又會忘記"},{"pid":"73a3d666c35b49505e5632408f1e908182e45abe","tid":2065023,"uid":78856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jm11eYT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJm11eYT.gif&h=b8068948&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8326256f0cc2fcd89453b278a1f07e79fee63963","tid":2065023,"uid":66283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"如果唔講打風可能有人命傷亡外<br />\n<br />\n我自己好鍾意打風落雨，感覺好平靜好舒服"},{"pid":"973c597268a99a06f8bf1f5a1e15fd5267f99b53","tid":2065023,"uid":232580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"只擔心水浸同街嘅小動物"}]}